top - shows a summary of the processes with associated commands.

df - reports file system storage usage.

dmesg - shows all messages about the kernel operations
 

iostat(input & output statistics) -shows CPU, input and output statistics for devices and partitions.

netstat - shows network connections

free - shows disk partition usage and indicates the free space.


cat /proc/cpuinfo - shows the information about the cpu 

cat /proc/meminfo- shows information of memory capacity.


